    <p><strong>Breed:</strong> Ragdoll Cat</p>
    <p><strong>Age:</strong> 12-15 years (average lifespan)</p>
    <p><strong>Size:</strong> Large</p>
    
    <h3>General Care Tips:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Grooming: Ragdolls require regular brushing to prevent their long fur from matting.</li>
        <li>Diet: Feed them high-quality, protein-rich food for their health and coat.</li>
        <li>Health: Ragdolls are prone to heart disease, so regular vet checkups are important.</li>
    </ul>

